data.description: LAKE OCONEE LIVING!!  5 Bedroom, 3 Full Bath,  Beautiful Ranch on full finished basement, minutes to Lake Oconee and Lake Oconee Parkway.  This gorgeous community offers a community boat ramp and dock. LOCATION LOCATION *** Minutes to the best of shopping and dining!!*** This home welcomes you with a covered rocking chair front porch,  step inside and you're immediately greeted by high valted ceiling in the large family area, hardwood flooring and gorgeous stacked stone fireplace, this space is open to large dining area,  you will be enjoying cooking and entertaining is this very large kitchen w abundance of cabinet and counter space.  Using our preferred lender you will receive a $2500 lender credit!!   The basement level is finished w a full bath and additional two bedrooms, plenty of storage and space in this home. There is an additional garge door on side/Basement area of home for your toys/boat etc The lot is private, level and has a fenced in back yard for your little ones and/or fur babies to run and play, additional space with outdoor storage building!! This home is perfect for large family, room mates, entertaining, ...schedule a tour of this gorgeous home and property and make this incredible home your own just in time for spring/summer to enjoy Lake Oconee and area!!! This home has been very well maintained with newer architectural roof and HVAC!! No Short Term Rental Restrictions
